      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 13.864,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "afe6577af9c",
        "adef89dd539"
      ],
      "end": 28.16,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 17.341,
      "text": "Competition in frontier AI is accelerating across coding, voice, and video. Moonshot AI has released Kimi K2.7 Code, an open-source model built for agentic coding tasks."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "adef89dd539",
        "a6e7f1fa2e2"
      ],
      "end": 44.002,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s4",
        "s5",
        "s6"
      ],
      "start": 28.16,
      "text": "Other firms are focusing on the sensory interfaces of AI. MiniMax launched Speech 2.8 to create more lifelike vocal synthesis for human-AI interaction. At the same time, Kuaishou has signaled new updates for its Kling AI video generation model."
    },
    {
      "end": 46.707,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 44.002,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 54.048,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 46.707,
      "text": "This afternoon will be cloudy with rain chances up to 55 percent and temperatures between 28 and 32 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 57.139,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 54.048,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 63.321,
      "id": "p7",
